Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞒着大家能看见妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伞飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啦  就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里啊  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  大概看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见我吗  人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,260)\fs80}浅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,500)\fs80}葱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(588,510)\fs80}{\c&H0025000}的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,525)\fs80}琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想碰人类  迫不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真没耐性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是钙 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我竟会…明明是人类还挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  不管了  这个身体我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  铜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类啊  请原谅他的无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葫芦里传出了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱  别说话  会累的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱  我听过这名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵的妖怪们聚集的幻之里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月森林里有一位美丽的苍琴师叫「浅葱」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个浅葱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但她身体抱恙以至无法继续弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送回了故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是面带笑容的人  完全没了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人类的孩子啊  为了浅葱你暂时将身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听话我就咬掉你的耳朵或鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手  低级的  他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狸猫咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许笑  地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻易接近妖怪肯定没好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况还要我借出身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是面带笑容的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得有点可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是早上才回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你的头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的颜色好像也变蓝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  早啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…早  北本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓…吓我一跳  一瞬间还以为认错了人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  这两人在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的辞典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一瞬间把夏目看成女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说北本  田沼感觉到什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:07:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你睡觉时让浅葱进入了你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像同化得很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  暂时请你合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晨的蓝色头发和眼睛就是附身现象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我叫他别这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无法阻止  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…你就是浅葱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要责备他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她从你身体里出来的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了强行驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能去实现浅葱的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望得到满足就会自然离开你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光说也没用  赶快实现愿望让我们回去吧  人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪来的  叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有讲给人类听的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你现在起就叫蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼伞的蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来接我们辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这狸猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的名字  太好了呢  蛇眼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱  怎么连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  不是很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才身体被占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你的  弹了琴就会离开我的身体了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要从制作琴开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为是特别的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种额头上有白线  跟鲤鱼长得一样  叫拉丝的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抓鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？少废话  别摆出副郁闷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱和蛇眼是什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  蛇眼是负责撑伞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月森林聚集了主人壬生大人看上的有才之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里为壬生大人和大家撑伞  并保护他们是蛇眼的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼很能干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月像梦境一般美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永远留在那里  一直待在壬生大人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远  永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能弹琴了就赶出来  真是心胸狭窄的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壬生大人收留了无处可去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了自己没用  我离开了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  这就是拉丝  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这就是要用来做琴弦的线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那材料收集就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  接下来是琴身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找树墩  而且上面要长着刚发芽的竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下  再等一下就能让你弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼真的对浅葱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么了  全身湿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  贵志会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  好好擦干  真的都湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永远留在那里  永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好刚空出来  快去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在这里待到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是…梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是浅葱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了吗  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  浅葱她睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟她说话的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱的手指已经不能弹琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体像干枯的泥土一样剥落的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但进入别的容器时恶化会变慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次看到她笑是在壬生大人面前弹琴  一脸幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在演奏中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤突然开始剥落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白修长的手指和发光的脸颊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在憧憬不已的壬生大人面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是满月  通往{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月的路会打开一会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想最后让她在壬生大人面前弹一次琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前请让她借用你的力量  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼为什么…为什么这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  铜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个撑伞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  怎么都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长竹子的树墩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在催情草的草丛中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我跟什么说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你了哦  作为交换我要拿走你的肠子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  跟奇怪的妖怪说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你在好好地找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  夏目  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  赶快动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体开始不舒服了  这种无力有点发热的感觉是浅葱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么弱的身体还去演奏  浅葱的生命会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  真对不起  都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来我都没确认过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱你想弹琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还有一次机会  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不灵巧  手指僵硬可能弹不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜他一直  一直对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜  怎么了  到底要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱  现在通往{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月的路还开放着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  然后为壬生大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好的  我来取你的肠子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴  浅葱和蛇眼重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那家伙赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  多亏你的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗  现在还能赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的话我来抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蛇眼  受了这样的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能弹我想再弹一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只为那位大人弹着琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果能再弹一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为了温柔的  我重要的朋友你弹一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜  你能听我弹琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远处听到了音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未听见过的美丽音符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:20:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音符从我的指尖流出  划开空气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像降落到空中一般  浅葱离开了我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带浅葱回故乡去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是睡得很深很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见了  浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了啊  老师  在人家辛苦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了吗  你这个烂好人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了  去给我买包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋还没开门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师有过想永远待下去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方我一辈子都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来一直这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  别抱我  放开  还不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着弹了留下的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那美丽的音符不再出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那音符不是出自我的手指  是出自她的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:50.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}猫咪徒然帐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师  你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会干这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了  给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我出去  夏目这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我掉进了洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天上掉下只白色小猪


